article.linkText: Moses has 15, UC Riverside downs Cal Poly 71-56
article.story: RIVERSIDE, Calif. -- — Isaiah Moses scored 15 points as UC Riverside beat Cal Poly 71-56 on Thursday. Moses added six rebounds for the Highlanders (7-10, 2/3 Big West Conference). Kaleb Smith scored 14 points and added nine rebounds. Kyle Owens and Nate Pickens both added 10 points. The Mustangs (4-13, 0-5) were led by Tuukka Jaakkola, who recorded 15 points. Cal Poly also got nine points and six rebounds from Quentin Jones. Aidan Prukop also put up nine points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
